  "Shoresh letter numbering convention": [
   {
    "text": "In Hebrew grammar, the shoresh פעל is used as a \"standard\" shoresh, and so sometimes the letters of פעל are used as names for the three shoresh positions: ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "type": "table",
